Using a prompting format based on the 'Detailed Guidelines' provides the most semantic similarity of all the techniques evaluated in this study. This finding indicates that providing both a detailed and explicit set of structured instructions creates a clearer framework within which the model can operate. However, using the 'Role-Based Expert' method increased stylistic improvements, but scored poorly in factual consistency compared to the 'Detailed Guidelines' method.

